Sonorous singer, Lisa Yaro is on an incredible journey to the limelight. Born in Kaduna, the Hausa-Fulani singer has garnered plaudits with multiple acting and executive producer credits. She has also starred in popular Netflix and cable films, earning her the multi-talented tag.<img class="size-full wp-image-1264256 aligncenter" src="https://i0.wp.com/cdn.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/lisa.jpg?resize=640%2C640&#038;ssl=1" alt="" width="640" height="640" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/cdn.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/lisa.jpg?w=1500&amp;ssl=1 1500w, https://i0.wp.com/cdn.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/lisa.jpg?resize=107%2C107&amp;ssl=1 107w, https://i0.wp.com/cdn.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/lisa.jpg?resize=300%2C300&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/cdn.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/lisa.jpg?resize=768%2C768&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/cdn.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/lisa.jpg?resize=1024%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/cdn.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/lisa.jpg?resize=58%2C58&amp;ssl=1 58w, https://i0.wp.com/cdn.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/lisa.jpg?resize=194%2C194&amp;ssl=1 194w, https://i0.wp.com/cdn.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/lisa.jpg?resize=130%2C130&amp;ssl=1 130w, https://i0.wp.com/cdn.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/lisa.jpg?resize=560%2C560&amp;ssl=1 560w, https://i0.wp.com/cdn.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/lisa.jpg?w=1280&amp;ssl=1 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px" data-recalc-dims="1" /> Lisa Yaro has modeling credit on numerous runways including the LA Fashion week and magazine features like Marie Westwood Magazine and EnVogue. Lisa Yaro is more than just an artist; she is art and this reflects in her music. “No Wahala” is a bouncy track that showcases Lisa’s vocal prowess and the melody in her music. This is Lisa Yaro’s 3rd single following up her second release “Mr. Lova”, which was up for Emmy consideration. Kanye West ‘Jesus is King’ album criticised by Christians(Opens in a new browser tab) Lisa Yaro is set to perform at the 6th Edition of the Afrimma Awards & Music Festival as well as host the Afrimma Fashion Show this October. The song “No Wahala” is produced by Award winning Nigerian-American producer Harmony “H-Money” Samuels who has production credits for the likes of Chris Brown, Ariana Grande, Ne-yo and Ciara. You can’t help but love this melodious song, Lisa wants “No Wahala”, just hit the play button and get into groove of the monster hit song “No Wahala”. Vanguard Mavin Records singer, Dija, has said that she will do everything within her power to always infuse her Hausa, Lebanese and Sierra-Leone culture into her music. October 4, 2015 In "Showtime People" Saturday, October 10 will not be forgotten in a hurry as it was the day, African artistes shut down the beautiful city of Dallas, Texas, United States for this year's Diasporan African Music Magazine Awards, AFRIMMA, which held at the historic Black Academy of Arts and Letters. November 5, 2015 In "Entertainment" Although, former MBGN 2005, Omowunmi Akinifesi completed her reign as beauty queen over five years ago, she has continued to enjoy public scrutiny. She has maintained a clean record, even as her style profile increased. Beautiful and elegant, Omonwumi puts her red carpet look together so effortlessly, that she is… February 6, 2011 In "Allure"